{"tid":510242,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"曾經有一段真摯的愛情擺在我面前","createTime":"2017-12-26T09:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T08:12:32.000Z","uid":116406,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1eb027392a30a8e42dda55df9ef505d9be17f17e","tid":510242,"uid":116406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T09:19:55.000Z","msg":"但我並沒有珍惜⋯<br />\n我同佢係連登識<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一切都係緣份既安排<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地渡過左好甜蜜既時光<br />\n我地好快咁成為左情侶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同普通情侶一樣<br />\n我地會拖手睇戲會抱實搭電梯會從後攬實佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但其實，單身兩年既我，一直都好怕再拍拖⋯⋯因為前一段感情傷害太深<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經令我變成一個棉花碰到都會受傷既懦夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平安夜個一日，我唔知痴左邊條線，突然提出想同佢做住朋友先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我唔想咁快cool死佢，佢仲有好多事情想做，我怕佢因爲我要放棄做自己想做的事情，將來會怪我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到個時感情太深既時候鬧分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會承受唔到<br />\n<br />\n可能個時我表達1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢誤會我對感情好兒嬉<br />\n最後分左手連朋友都冇得做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家我可以搵佢既途徑都冇晒了⋯⋯<br />\n唯一希望佢可以睇到依個post，比個機會我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾經有一段真摯的愛情擺在我面前但我並沒有珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位手足珍惜眼前人 要勇敢地去愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f80536dd8ff86ffcbe5dde40b9892b0c436500","tid":510242,"uid":53794,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T09:20:46.000Z","msg":"自己on9"},{"pid":"caa