score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T13:18:54.000Z","msg":"出緊去<br />\n去佢到要坐個半鐘車<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一路搭車一路幻想可以見番佢<br />\n個心好酸"},{"pid":"6f9f1a87eb4e0aa2590adc991964b317986e93d6","tid":510242,"uid":116406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T14:14:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> bb你去左邊"},{"pid":"66b628a4941a4896a78ce62efffc0e69d2cb0e22","tid":510242,"uid":116406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T15:31:43.000Z","msg":"Mola mola<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c7144515d32796a3417b5d896ab626c727fb9d","tid":510242,"uid":116406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T22:19:21.000Z","msg":"佢仲係唔肯睇我msg..."},{"pid":"25ebee63c9587022b9b8f0cf5c5bbf3c72befa8f","tid":510242,"uid":116406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:12:32.000Z","msg":"佢block晒我啲contact 了<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nI miss her"}]}